package newco.crm

//-----------------------
// Request
//-----------------------
Request is a record
    - with one customerName: Text
    - with zero or one loyaltyLevel: LoyaltyLevel
    - with zero or more products (product): Product

LoyaltyLevel is an ordered enumeration with domain:
    'Silver', 'Gold', 'Platinum'

Product is a record
    - with one id: Text
    - with one price: Number


//-----------------------
// Response
//-----------------------
Response is a record
    - with one discount: Number                     // discount applicable to the shopping cart
    - with one loyaltyPointIncrement: Integer
    - with one message: Text